### Create account
POST http://localhost:8080/payments/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-1"
}

### Deposit
POST http://localhost:8080/payments/accounts/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-1",
  "amount": 2000
}

