POST http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-1",
  "amount": 1500,
  "description": "Headphones"
}

### List orders
GET http://localhost:8080/orders?user_id=user-1

### Get order
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/1

